Lightweight Framework, designed to work with the following folder structure for your sites.

It is conveniently ignored by the repository enabling you to trigger your own git repository for just the files/folders neccessary to run the site, but also allowing you to clone the framework repository for future updates and changes to be pulled in.

Your application will sit within the a application/ folder something like below.

	application/
		controller/
		model/
		view/
		themes/
		library/
	assets/
	
